description: Saved the night of her execution, Asphodel finds solace with Lenny, her karate partner. Asphodel tells Lenny about childhood trauma due to the methods of a particularly cruel scientist. Condemned for its barbaric practices, it was never to hurt her, yet her pain still lingers.
name: The Scar

description: Bowman is preparing to put the finishing touches to his crazy scheme: subjugate Satan and release all its power on the world of men. Friends of Asphodel plan to infiltrate the ceremony during which Bowman will reveal his apocalyptic project.
name: Reminiscences

description: Prisoner of Dr. Bowman, Asphodel is preparing to attend the opening of the gates of Hell. Andrew Lenny and the wizard infiltrate Bowman's underground base. They move, step by step, advancing in hostile territory.
name: The Indictment

description: The Batgirls are back! Check out what’s burning in Burnside on the home front...featuring Lois Lane! Batgirls part 1 of 3.
name: The Batgirls Swing Again! Part 1 of 3

description: The Infinite Comic that will have everyone talking! Full of fun, heart, and pranks, this is one folks'll be talking about for years!
name: The Return of the Phoenix

volume.name: A Year of Marvels: April Infinite Comic

description: Kochikame (special chapter of the series, usually appearing in Weekly Shonen Jump, in honor of its 35th anniversary)
